channel.title: Connection Help
channel.description:
Okay, so I just recently created an RSPS and everything was fine for about one day. Everyone was able to connect there was no lag etc.
But, the next day I got complaints from everyone on the server that they were unable to connect even though I had my server running.
I was wondering If anyone else had the same problems and also if anyone could help.
Thanks in advance!
